attributes.background:
Given that:
- The original limit of 28 days was reached through agreement in the House of Commons;
- The original limit of 28 days has not been reached in any case to date;
- Extension of this limit constitutes a grave attack on the civil liberties of all citizens of this country;

The signatories of this petition request that the recently-announced plans to extend the limit to 42 days be abandoned, as it does not have public support, and is completely unnecessary.
